  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Revelations is a zombies passion project created solely by me, Brock de Beaubien. It's heavily inspired by bo2 and bo3 zombies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-round based zombies horde shooter</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-tons of guns</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-story</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-atmosphere</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-perks</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-varying enemy types</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-different map locations</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-weapon upgrades</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Revelations will continue to be enhanced.   I am dedicated to create more maps, weapons, repair bugs, and quality of life changes to create a more polished project for all players. </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Revelations is a zombies passion project created solely by me, Brock de Beaubien. It's heavily inspired by bo2 and bo3 zombies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-round based zombies horde shooter</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-tons of guns</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-story</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-atmosphere</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-perks</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-varying enemy types</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-different map locations</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-weapon upgrades</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Revelations will continue to be enhanced.   I am dedicated to create more maps, weapons, repair bugs, and quality of life changes to create a more polished project for all players. </p>",
